/**
 * <p><b>Title:</b><br/>
 * StyleWidget
 * </p>
 *
 * <p><b>Description:</b><br/>
 *	Widget for controlling styler options for a DataItem.  Note that I 
 *  used a trial version of SWTDesigner to build portions of this widget.     
